## Unlock Deeper Observability

Enterprise-Grade OpenTelemetry for superior application performance monitoring.

- Accelerate [![OpenTelemetry](https://img.shields.io/badge/OpenTelemetry-111?logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](https://github.com/open-telemetry) implementation with [![Odigos](https://img.shields.io/badge/Odigos-111?logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](https://github.com/odigos-io)
- An [![eBPF](https://img.shields.io/badge/eBPF-111?logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](https://github.com/cilium/ebpf)-based solution providing zero-performance overhead for deeper tracing.
- Zero-code implentation!
